  "title": "Mechatronics Engineer (Junior)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities (Junior)</strong></p><p>· Assist senior engineers in installation and commissioning activities</p><p>· Perform routine maintenance and basic troubleshooting</p><p>· Support testing and inspection of equipment</p><p>· Maintain and update records and reports</p><p>· Learn system operations and company procedures</p><p>· Provide on-site technical support when required</p><p><strong>Job Requirements (Junior)</strong></p><p>· Diploma or Degree in Mechatronics, Mechanical, Electrical, or related field</p><p>· Fresh graduates are welcome to apply</p><p>· Basic knowledge of:</p><ul><li>Mechanical systems</li><li>Electrical wiring and components</li><li>Sensors and actuators</li><li>PLC or basic automation (advantage)</li></ul><p>· Willingness to learn and take guidance</p><p>· Good teamwork and communication skills</p><p>· Able to travel to project sites if required</p>",
